===Etymology===
From the {{etyl|la}} preposition ''[[trans#Latin|trans]]'' (meaning "[[across]]") + ''[[silvam]]'', the {{accusative}} {{singular}} of ''[[silva]]'' meaning "[[forest]]". Meaning "across the forest".

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/tɹænslˈveɪniə/}}
* {{rhymes|eɪniə}}

